1. create an account
2. Login
3. update your profile
4. Feed Page - Explore
5. Send Connection Request
6. See our Matches
7. See the request we have sent/recieved
8. update your profile  

LLD
-> DB Design
    -> User Profile(FN, LN, EmailID, Password, age, Gender)
    -> ConnectionRequest(from_uid, to_uid,status)
     
-> API Design {REST API}
    ->GET API(fetch)
    ->POST API(send)
    ->PUT API(update the data)
    ->PATCH API(UPDATE THE DATA, SLIGHTLY DIFFERENT THAN PUT)
    ->DELETE API

->TYPES OF API:
    ->POST/SIGNUP
    ->POST/LOGIN
    ->GET/PROFILE
    ->POST/PROFILE
    ->PATCH/PROFILE
    ->DELETE/PROFILE
    ->POST/SENDREQUEST
    ->POST/OVERVIEWREQUEST
    ->GET/REQUEST
    ->GET/CONNECTION
